    # - `OPar_CSym_Space_1234_Comma_567_Period_89_CPar`<br>
    #   `($ 1234,567.89)`
    # - `CSym_Space_Minus_12_Comma_34_Comma_567_Period_89`<br>
    #   `$ -12,34,567.89`
    # - `CSym_Minus_12_Comma_34_Comma_567_Period_89`<br>
