    # - `Minus_1_Comma_234_Comma_567_Period_89_Space_CSym`<br>
    #   `-1,234,567.89 $`
    # - `Minus_CSym_Space_1_Comma_234_Comma_567_Period_89`<br>
    #   `-$ 1,234,567.89`
