    # - `OPar_1_Comma_234_Comma_567_Period_89_Space_CSym_CPar`<br>
    #   `(1,234,567.89 $)`
    # - `OPar_1_Period_234_Period_567_Comma_89_Space_CSym_CPar`<br>
    #   `(1.234.567,89 $)`
    # - `OPar_1_Space_234_Space_567_Comma_89_CSym_CPar`<br>
